com.github.nodamushi.common.paths.NPaths.Visit

    • com.github.nodamushi.common.pathsでのNPaths.Visitの使用

      NPaths.Visit型のパラメータを持つcom.github.nodamushi.common.pathsのメソッド 
      修飾子とタイプ メソッドと説明
      static void NPaths.walkDirectories(Path start, int directoryMaxDepth, NPaths.Visit visitDirectory)
      only implements FileVisitor.preVisitDirectory(Object, BasicFileAttributes),and call Files.walkFileTree(Path, FileVisitor).
      static void NPaths.walkFiles(Path start, int directoryMaxDepth, NPaths.Visit visitFile)
      only implements FileVisitor.visitFile(Object, BasicFileAttributes),and call Files.walkFileTree(Path, FileVisitor).
